### RawSQL & Transaction API Endpoints


@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/rawsql-trans

###############################################
# 1. RAW SQL DEMO
# Lấy danh sách giáo viên có lương cao hơn mức cho trước
###############################################

### Danh sách giáo viên có lương cao hơn 2000
GET {{apiUrl}}/high-earners?minSalary=2000

###############################################
# 2. MIXED QUERY DEMO  
# Kết hợp Raw SQL và Query Builder
###############################################

### Danh sách giáo viên sinh trước năm 1975
GET {{apiUrl}}/born-before/1975

###############################################
# 3. TRANSACTION DEMO
# Chuyển lương giữa 2 giáo viên với transaction
###############################################

### Chuyển 500 lương từ giáo viên "002" sang "001"
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "002",
  "toTeacherId": "001",
  "amount": 500
}

###############################################
# Transaction Rollback Demo
###############################################
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer-rollback-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "002",
  "toTeacherId": "001",
  "amount": 500
}


###############################################
# Các trường hợp lỗi - Transaction Demo
###############################################

### Lỗi: Lương không đủ (insufficient salary)
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "001",
  "toTeacherId": "002",
  "amount": 999999
}

### Lỗi: Chuyển lương cho chính mình (same teacher)
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "001",
  "toTeacherId": "001",
  "amount": 100
}

### Lỗi: Giáo viên không tồn tại (teacher not found)
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "999",
  "toTeacherId": "001",
  "amount": 100
}

### Lỗi: Thiếu tham số (missing parameters)
POST {{apiUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromTeacherId": "001",
  "amount": 100
}
